{"tid":808917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果》再揭☭高鐵☭西九站暗藏「後勤用地」 運房局深夜玩自爆","createTime":"2018-09-06T17:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T01:59:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a500a6e36f66ae4e5d505b5e888b8e9eaf96a21a","tid":808917,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180907/large/1536251005_89a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536251005_89a3.png&h=637b2e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n☭高鐵☭西九龍站通車在即，惟公眾至日前才知悉該站暗藏逾3萬呎的B5層空間。《蘋果》翻查圖則再發現 ，原來B4層與B3層之間，亦有一層B4M層（Basement 4M），面積達4.5萬方呎，過去同樣鮮有被提及。《蘋果》早前就此向港鐵查詢，獲告之周五下午回覆，惟運房局周四深夜突然自我引爆。<br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果》取得的2017年3月修訂圖則，B4M層位於B3、B4之間的間隔牆內，呈長條形狀，設一條長約500米的通道貫通。4.5萬方呎的空間內有約18間獨立房間，除了一般機電用途房間外，有多間房的圖則名稱包括「MTR Staff」字眼，相信只供港鐵人員使用，當中包括控制室、會面室、貯物櫃室等等。唯獨男女廁、以及另一間「列車人員訪談室（Train Staff Interview Room）」，圖則名稱上未有列明只供港鐵使用。本報就此向港鐵查詢，但未有向運房局提問。<br />\n<br />\n惟運房局在昨深夜11時02分再次透過政府新聞處發稿，自爆西九龍站內樓層與樓層之間，設有「後勤用地」，分別位於B1售票大堂之上的「B1M」層（5,600平方米）、位於B2入境層之上的「B2H」層（10,300平方米）、位於B3出境層之上的「B3M／B3H」層（7,200平方米）和位於B4月台層之上的「B4M」層（4,200平方米），合共29.4萬呎。局方解釋，有關後勤用地專供放置站內設施，和供廣深港☭高鐵☭香港段營運商人員辦公之用，由港鐵公司負責管理，強調這些後勤用地均不屬「內地口岸區」範圍。<br />\n<br />\n運房局稱，有關用地設有抽風管道、鐵路營運商辦公室、冷氣系統機房設施和垃圾收集用房等，強調有關用地的出入口，均有保安設施上鎖，並會嚴格控制及派員巡邏，禁止未獲授權人士進入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180907/large/1536251024_f7aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536251024_f7aa.png&h=7c810172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180907/large/1536251025_8145.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536251025_8145.png&h=6f68a797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180907/large/1536251835_fb51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536251835_fb51.jpg&h=aba953a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c7e94f7772df1618e3dc600b37649ff4e3bcf82","tid":808917,"uid":36077,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"7386c7a4100a26e57b5cf19bcb0e771739f80371","tid":808917,"uid":16676,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://blog.ylib.com/public/Utilities/ImageReader.aspx?/c/3/c3e1fadd-f847-492a-9719-355a00e528f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.ylib.com%2Fpublic%2FUtilities%2FImageReader.aspx%3F%2Fc%2F3%2Fc3e1fadd-f847-492a-9719-355a00e528f1.jpg&h=f9cb55a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.ylib.com/public/Utilities/ImageReader.aspx?/c/b/cb410e3a-878f-4c97-91e4-3b1c19627f45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.ylib.com%2Fpublic%2FUtilities%2FImageReader.aspx%3F%2Fc%2Fb%2Fcb410e3a-878f-4c97-91e4-3b1c19627f45.jpg&h=762a089f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-px4JvLtttiI/VIGkSmxmt-I/AAAAAAAAA-0/neO9izY46Go/s1600/SAM_0208%2B(800x600).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-px4JvLtttiI%2FVIGkSmxmt-I%2FAAAAAAAAA-0%2FneO9izY46Go%2Fs1600%2FSAM_0208%252B%28800x600%29.jpg&h=5f2b019d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9&frac34;月台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde2ab286abc85eeaa4905db63dfff567525e07b","tid":808917,"uid":26773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"爆左咁多又點 咪又係如常通車"},{"pid":"f6dae386f1c96e755bf66e234f1ac8062fd63394","tid":808917,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"西九大監獄"},{"pid":"7e230e05e3